%p Hello,

%p== #{@comment.user.name} <#{@comment.user.email}> has made a new comment on the #{@comment.commentable.name} #{@comment.commentable.class.to_s.titleize}:

%p= @comment.comment

%p To view/respond to it, please visit the url below:

- if @comment.commentable.is_a?(DataResponse)
  %p= link_to projects_url, projects_url
- else
  %p= link_to activity_url(@comment.commentable), activity_url(@comment.commentable)

= render 'signature'
